    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Trapezionida psylla (Macpherson, 1994), ovigerous female (cl 5.3 mm), JAMSTEC 106858. A, carapace, pleomeres 1–3, eyes and antennal peduncles, dorsal view; B, thoracic sternum, ventral view; C, left antennular peduncle basal article, ventral view; D, left antennal peduncle, ventral view; E, right maxilliped 3 merus, lateral view; F, right cheliped, merus and carpus, dorsal view (setae omitted); G, same, chela, dorsal view (setae omitted)." ;
