    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Trapezionida psylla (Macpherson, 1994), ovigerous female (cl 5.3 mm), JAMSTEC 106858. A, right pereopod 2, outer view; B, same, dactylus, outer view; C, right pereopod 3, outer view; D, right pereopod 4, outer view." ;
